title: DAZ3D The Torch and Construction Kit
description:
---Previously uploaded to KAT by DAZalot---

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/33085

The Torch and construction set is the must have item for everyone who needs a torch. Plain and simple. You get 11 different torches to light your scenes plus a complete set of props to build your own. These torches were modeled from actual flames and not just texture wrapped and the emission light was real world measured so no worrying about adjusting dials.
